Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:45.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:48.23,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:52.05,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}思うまま書き滑らせて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:57.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}描く未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.59,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}澄み渡る空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:09.10,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}果てしないほど青く
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:13.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無邪気な心に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:16.72,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充たされ魅かれてく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:20.68,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やがて自由に飛びまわれる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:23.72,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}翼を手に入れて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:28.22,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無垢な瞳は求めてく
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:32.02,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}空の向こうへ　行きたいな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:35.12,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}止め処ない願いから
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:38.47,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一つだけ叶うのなら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:42.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰にも譲りたくはない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:46.21,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夢を掴みたいと思うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:49.42,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}子供の頃の夢は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:52.69,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}色褪せない落書きで
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:56.62,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつまでも描き続けられた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:04:01.72,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}願う未来へとつながる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:45.00,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童时的那个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.16,0:02:48.23,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.44,0:02:52.05,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}随心所欲地去描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.05,0:02:57.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己描绘的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.59,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}万里无云的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:09.10,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无边无际的蔚蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:13.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}纯洁无瑕的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.34,0:03:16.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}充盈着无限魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:20.68,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}终于能自由翱翔于天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:23.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}长出了美丽的羽翼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:28.22,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}无瑕的瞳孔在寻求
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:32.02,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想去那天空的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:35.12,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在那无数的愿望中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:38.47,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}若是只有一个能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:42.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不愿让给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:46.21,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要紧紧抓住那梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.22,0:03:49.42,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孩童时的那个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:52.69,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是永不退色的涂鸦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:56.62,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}永不停息地去描写
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.62,0:04:01.72,OPCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走向自己祈愿的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,780)\fad(1000,8)\3a&00&\3c&0000A0&}永远的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:44.33,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}炎さえも凍てついた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:50.99,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}孤独の中求む
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.99,0:21:59.65,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}魂から結びつき
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.87,0:22:07.68,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}私を恋い暖めて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:16.50,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　祈りの言葉がふるえ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:24.21,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嗚呼　弱きいのちが消えても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:32.08,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえす　輪廻の流れ辿り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.19,0:22:40.70,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終わらない世界の宿命を見つめてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.76,0:22:48.20,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}くりかえし　詠われる者達よ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.21,0:22:56.34,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}守られてまどろむ宵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.88,0:21:44.33,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就算火焰都冻结
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:50.99,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}也在孤独中寻求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.99,0:21:59.65,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}请用灵魂连结我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.87,0:22:07.68,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}请用爱恋温暖我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.83,0:22:16.50,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}呜呼 那颤抖的祈愿之声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:24.21,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}呜呼 那脆弱的生命消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:32.08,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}追溯那不断交替的轮回之流
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.19,0:22:40.70,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}凝望那永不终结的世界的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.76,0:22:48.20,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不断轮回的 那些传颂之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.21,0:22:56.34,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}被守护着安眠的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.59,0:00:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.85,0:00:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长 那些人怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管了 代替他们的人要多少有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船 船长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.60,0:01:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.38,0:01:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀…杀…杀了她
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船？ 在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来迟了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.97,0:02:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.91,0:02:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好惨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这家伙干的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳·托库的船？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳·托库记得是位于南面的国家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.98,0:04:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风闻是个不怎么样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是风闻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们绑架人 并通过将其买卖获取国家利益
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:05:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 昨晚遇难的那艘船也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错了 兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头颈上挂着很大锁链的女人也可以证明这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.98,0:05:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸存的只有她一人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.01,0:05:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在把她扔进大牢里了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大牢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.69,0:05:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是把船员们全都杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,处理事情时还是得谨慎一些
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在说我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.11,0:05:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙 什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你这家伙」算什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有「卡露拉」这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.25,0:05:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士兵怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.20,0:05:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人的话正在睡午觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把他们打倒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.12,0:05:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有一手的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.05,0:05:47.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是像这样把船员们杀尽的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.93,0:05:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他们应得的报应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.83,0:05:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.82,0:05:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.76,0:05:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是这个国家的皇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.36,0:05:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎么处理我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.01,0:06:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引渡给纳·托库吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是 在这里就杀了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别这么着急要结论
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:12.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先养一养伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.04,0:06:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人挺有趣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.74,0:06:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藏匿那个人 真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.64,0:06:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是让纳·托库国知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄不好就等于给了他们侵略我国的口实
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是纳·托库国有那意思的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要找到借口还不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.37,0:07:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 更让我担心的是希剀里佩齐穆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后会有期
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道 圣上您…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不幸中的万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.59,0:07:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流落到的是这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以哈克奥罗先生的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.14,0:07:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是不会把卡露拉引渡给纳·托库的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 皇就是那样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.34,0:07:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能请你脱掉衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说衣服 请你脱掉衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你有那方面的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 才不是 才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是想看看你还有没有别的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉是哪个国家的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是在雅玛优拉出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个国家边境的小村落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然什么都没有 但却是个非常好的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.68,0:08:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 现在都怎么样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:56.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国家？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的东西我早忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这锁链 帮你卸下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁链？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这里不是纳·托库啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然感谢你的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我想那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事不试试看怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 艾露露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是叫艾露露吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你那份心意就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望把那家伙从牢里放出来？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.75,0:09:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么 那家伙可是杀了很多人的危险人物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.44,0:10:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉不是毫无理由就会杀人的人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都和她见面自然就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不可以在未经允许的情况下出城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.61,0:10:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是传出奇怪的谣言就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的妹妹阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露 她是卡露拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多多关照 阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.42,0:10:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.50,0:11:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是项链 最近流行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:10.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,项链？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.89,0:11:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给阿露露也做一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.67,0:11:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个这样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样穿过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉原来很心灵手巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和外表不相符？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.44,0:12:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就会给你准备房间的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.49,0:12:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我住在那个大牢里就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.60,0:12:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样倒是更能安下心来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那样…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.61,0:12:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 能带点酒过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微一点就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这倒是没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这… 那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美味的酒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腰部力量不够
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.70,0:13:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你可以从大牢里出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.42,0:13:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 要不要和我来一场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那家伙 据说一人杀了好几十人的剑奴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外表可爱 却又真是个危险的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都和那么多人打过了 你应该不讨厌战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.48,0:13:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.84,0:13:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下 恳请您重新定夺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大神教会的巫女去当国师 前所未闻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.65,0:13:50.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡事都得有先例
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且国师是维持世界均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进而从灾难中保护人民的伟大工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.87,0:14:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这一次作为国师正式来此赴任的乌露特莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.82,0:14:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是作为辅佐的神结
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国师？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小阿露
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.47,0:14:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去小柚那里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要承蒙照顾了 艾露露姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.12,0:15:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把那家伙正式分配到部下？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希剀里佩齐穆有可疑的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.71,0:15:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在通过国师和边临小国也取得了联系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:28.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为了以防万一 增加兵力是当务之急
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样 也不用把那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我赞成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.67,0:15:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,功夫看来也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但始终是外人 不能信任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.53,0:15:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 我可不是那种忘恩负义的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙又擅自…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.83,0:15:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的皇救了我的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我至少要为此报答他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.96,0:16:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我怎么说原来也是剑奴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在战场上 应该会派得上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先让我们见识一下你的实力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 我来做对手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.06,0:16:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 能让我来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来做对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大将你？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让武士大将亲自出马真是我的荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:39.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人真的想和武士大将过招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.64,0:16:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有自知之明也要有个限度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 似乎变得有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许能看见大将久违的动真格的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不摆架势吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.71,0:17:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然接下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的确是剑奴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.01,0:17:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但剑奴也有剑奴的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想和未尽全力的人战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说大将未尽全力？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.91,0:17:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就全力以赴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.92,0:17:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样才对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则就没趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.64,0:18:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.54,0:18:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会让你后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉的武器做好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.81,0:19:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 但是稍稍有点问题
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.78,0:19:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡露拉大人的要求是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不会断 绝不会弯 绝不会破损的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.95,0:20:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铸剑师也是第一次打造这样的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 为了绝不会破损而将锋利程度放在了其后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以也比较钝…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确这样的话既不会断也不会弯 但…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我订的东西似乎做好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 做是做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.44,0:20:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是拿起来都很勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种东西根本派不上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去试一试剑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.47,0:21:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.03,0:21:10.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有破损 确认
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.54,0:21:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合我的胃口 那我就收下了


